            "state": "hidden",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "s_intro_sub",
                "text": "滕子京谪守巴陵郡，政通人和，百废具兴，重修岳阳楼。",
                "emoji": "🏰",
                "state": "hidden",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "s_scenery",
            "text": "第二段：洞庭胜状",
            "emoji": "🌊",
            "state": "hidden",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "s_scenery_sub",
                "text": "浩浩汤汤，横无际涯；北通巫峡，南极潇湘；迁客骚人会此览物。",
                "emoji": "⛵",
                "state": "hidden",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "s_rainy",
            "text": "第三段：淫雨霏霏 (阴冷悲凉)",
            "emoji": "⛈️",
            "state": "hidden",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "s_rainy_sub",
                "text": "日星隐曜，樯倾楫摧；登楼则有去国怀乡、忧谗畏讥之悲感。",
                "emoji": "😢",
                "state": "hidden",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "s_sunny",
            "text": "第四段：春和景明 (晴朗喜悦)",
            "emoji": "☀️",
            "state": "hidden",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "s_sunny_sub",
                "text": "上下天光，一碧万顷，浮光跃金；登楼则心旷神怡、宠辱偕忘之喜悦。",
                "emoji": "😊",
                "state": "hidden",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "s_philosophy",
            "text": "第五段：古仁人之心",
            "emoji": "⚖️",
            "state": "hidden",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "s_philosophy_sub",
                "text": "不以物喜，不以己悲；先天下之忧而忧，后天下之乐而乐。",
                "emoji": "🌟",
                "state": "hidden",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
